latestPosts.caption:
Looking for a romantic date spot or a fun place to hang out with your gang? 😍
De Little Venice in Surat is a floating restaurant that offers unforgettable vibes, delicious multi-cuisine food, and stunning views – perfect for pre-wedding shoots or grand celebrations! 💒✨
🍽️ From Punjabi to Italian, they’ve got it all!
🛶 With seating on water and a banquet for 800+ guests, this is more than just a meal – it’s a whole experience.
✨ Bonus: Food is served after the Aarti of Hanuman Dada 🙏
Tag your loved ones and plan your next outing here! 💕
